<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>DISK FULL WARNING</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      max-width: 700px;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .warning-logo {
      width: 350px;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .warning-disk {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: red;
      font-size: 44px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.7;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .important {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .disk-usage {
      color: red;
      font-size: 34px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .log-button {
      background-color: red;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      font-size: 18px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .log-button:hover {
      background-color: #b30000;
    }

    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .content-section {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      width: 100%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-section">
      <img src="cid:warninglogo" alt="SYSNET DEF V1.0" class="warning-logo">
      <img src="cid:disklogo" alt="Disk Full" class="warning-disk">
      <h1>DISK FULL!!!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <p>The current disk usage has exceeded the safe threshold and may cause system instability or data loss. Please free up some space immediately.</p>
      <p class="important">Time: <%= time %></p>
      <div class="disk-usage">Disk Usage: <%= diskUsage %>%</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <form action="/disk-log">
        <button class="log-button">DISK LOG</button>
      </form>
      <p>Clicking on the button will take you to the disk usage log page.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      ACRONICS SOLUTIONS Inc. All Rights Reserved<br>
      03 Quang Trung, Hai Chau 1, Hai Chau, Da Nang
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
